structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS
FINANCE AND REVENUE OF CITIES OTHER THAN THE FIRST CLASS

law.history: Repealed 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 434, sec. 15, effective July 15, 1982; amended ch. 141, sec. 51. -- Amended 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 386, sec. 17. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 3187a, 3416, 3417, 3544a-8, 3544a-9, 3544a-13, 3544a-14.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Report of tax sales in cities of second, third and fourth classes -- Certificate to purchaser -- Notice to owner.
metadata.lrc-note: . This section was amended by 1982 Acts Chapter 141, Section 51 and repealed by 1982 Acts Chapter 434, Section 15. Pursuant to KRS 446.260, the repeal prevails.
metadata.note: 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 396, sec. 54 would also have amended this section effective July 1, 1982. However, 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 396 was repealed by 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 141, sec. 146, also effective July 1, 1982.
